name: Bunny Scout #2814 Activate!
description: Stress levels are at an all time high.  The apocalypse is coming.  Just yesterday, meteors have been crashing through earth's atmosphere and Hell is appearing on Earth.  Prophecy predicts that only an elite group of mythical heroes can stop this impending doom, but can Aokuma and friends activate the last mythical hero's pod in time to save the world? Bunny Scout #2814, Activate!
